{"ts":"2026-06-27T01:05:50.603Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Clarifying The Scope**\n\nOkay, the admin page concept needs a revisit. Currently, I don't see a dedicated admin section within `app/admin`. I'm going to center my efforts on building the private app design system, for login, the client portal, and the admin portal, but *not* touch the public landing page. The focus here is on reusable frontend UI.\n\n\n**Refining The Components**\n\nI'm now focusing on creating primitives specifically for authenticated product screens. The goal is a premium, 2026 enterprise AI operations feel, not a generic admin template. All components will be responsive, accessible, and keyboard-friendly, while scoped to avoid affecting the public landing page. I've located the client portal under `app/portal/page.tsx` and am examining how the login state works within `ClientWorkspace.tsx`, where `authed === false` triggers the login box.\n\n\n**Designing The GFF Admin**\n\nI'm now diving into the specifics of the `app/admin/page.tsx` file. My goal is a truly advanced admin control panel. It should include everything from agent health logs and user activity to system usage analytics and a robust governance panel. I'm also planning the new component directory `/components/private-app/index.tsx`, where all the premium components will reside, starting with the `SecurePreviewNotice` component, a sandbox workspace alert.\n\n\n**Defining UI Components**\n\nI'm now focusing on specific components for the admin interface, starting with a `SecureEnclaveNotice` component for secure areas. I envision this as a pulsing lock icon, dark background with neon-like borders, and clean typography. The `UserAvatar` displays profile details and security tier with a green online indicator and hover card. I'm also planning a `NotificationBell` with real-time security event notifications, and a `RoleSwitcherPreview` with a cryptographic animation for role changes. Finally, I'm designing `WorkspaceBreadcrumbs` with fine lines and custom separators.\n\n\n**Constructing The Interface**\n\nI'm now detailing some key UI elements. I'm designing a sleek `CommandButton` for quick access, and a comprehensive `PrivateSidebar` for navigation. I'm also planning a `PrivateTopbar` layout to consolidate critical controls. In addition, there's a `PrivatePageHeader` for page-specific details, as well as a reusable `WorkspaceCard` and `MetricTile` for data presentation.\n\n\n**Expanding UI Library**\n\nI'm now detailing some more key UI elements for the private interface, including a `StatusBadge` for showing real-time system states. I'm also planning a `DataTable`, a `FilterBar`, and an `EmptyState` component. I'm additionally designing an `ActivityFeed` for security event logging and a `Timeline` for workflow visualization, alongside a `DocumentCard` for document display.\n\n\n**Expanding Private UI**\n\nI'm now focusing on several key components, including an `InvoiceCard` for ledger details and cryptographic validation, and a `SupportTicketCard` with SLA timers and priority levels. I'm also planning an `AnalyticsPanel` with custom SVGs for resource usage, a `GovernancePanel` for compliance and policy control, and an `AgentHealthCard` to show agent vital stats. There's also a `ProjectCard` for sandbox space details and a `PrivateAppShell` layout wrapper. This should create a rich experience!\n\n\n**Adding The Command Palette**\n\nI'm now integrating a command palette. I'm excited about `WorkspaceCommandButton` triggering an interactive modal. This modal, designed for the private app shell, will be accessible via a click or `âŒ˜K`/`Ctrl+K`. I've verified that existing files won't be overwritten. I'm also confirming the directive to build in the private app design system. I will start by creating `components/private-app/index.tsx`.\n\n\n**Outlining Design Principles**\n\nI'm now writing a detailed plan. I'm focusing on crafting a story of cryptographic security and sovereign control for the GFF Enclaves. My visual metaphor is \"Monolithic Zero-Trust Terminal,\" using monochromatic obsidian palettes and fine hairlines. I envision a split-pane layout with a sticky sidebar, slim topbar, and a spacious main content area for rich content.\n\n\n**Defining Mobile Interactions**\n\nI'm now detailing interaction and mobile strategies. I'm prioritizing a command palette, custom spotlights, and micro-interactive changes. Mobile will feature slide-out menus, horizontal data table scrolling with indicators, and grid adaptation from three to one column with generous tap targets.\n\nI have a concrete list of files to change, and files to create.\n\n\n**Drafting The Components**\n\nI'm now fully immersed in coding. I'll meticulously craft each component within `components/private-app/index.tsx`, ensuring clean TypeScript, standard Lucide icons, and smooth CSS transitions. I'm leveraging `motion/react` for elegant micro-motions, importing `motion` and `AnimatePresence`. My focus is on crafting the first component: `SecurePreviewNotice`. I'm starting from scratch.\n\n\n**Implementing The Spotlight**\n\nI'm now implementing the spotlight effect using native radial gradients. I'm leveraging `useRef` to track the mouse position within a div and updating a state variable for position. I've designed the spotlight to be lightweight, using a transparent white gradient for a subtle glow. This looks very nice on dark backgrounds! I'm ready to continue building components and will soon refine component matching.\n\n\n\n**Defining Component Breakdown**\n\nI'm now breaking down component needs. `PrivateAppShell` will orchestrate layout with children. `PrivateSidebar` requires dynamic navigation. `PrivateTopbar` needs a search bar, bell, and breadcrumbs. `PrivatePageHeader` must handle actions, and `WorkspaceBreadcrumbs` needs clean trails. `WorkspaceCommandButton` will trigger a command palette. `WorkspaceCard` will act as a container.\n\n\n**Refining Spotlight Design**\n\nI'm now refining the spotlight effect with glassmorphic styling, and adding the following components: `MetricTile` (animated sparklines), `StatusBadge`, `DataTable`, `FilterBar`, `EmptyState`, `ActivityFeed`, `Timeline`, `DocumentCard`, `InvoiceCard`, `SupportTicketCard`, `AnalyticsPanel`, `GovernancePanel`, `AgentHealthCard`, `ProjectCard` and `UserAvatar`.\n\n\n**Expanding Component Suite**\n\nI'm now detailing some core components: a `NotificationBell` with interactive reading states for system events, a `RoleSwitcherPreview` featuring a terminal-like authorization animation, and a persistent `SecurePreviewNotice` banner for zero-trust validation. I will also make sure that `motion/react` and `lucide-react` are accessible within the code, and start writing out `components/private-app/index.tsx`, with interactive search and live metrics.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T01:05:50.623Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"iarrqwbw","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/components/private-app/index.tsx","new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState, useEffect, useRef, useId } from \"react\";\nimport Link from \"next/link\";\nimport { motion, AnimatePresence } from \"motion/react\";\nimport { \n  Lock, Shield, Key, CheckCircle, RefreshCw, Layers, FileText, \n  CreditCard, CheckSquare, MessageSquare, BarChart3, ShieldCheck, \n  Cpu, ArrowRight, UserCheck, AlertCircle, HelpCircle, Download, Activity,\n  Search, Bell, ChevronRight, Menu, X, Settings, LogOut, Terminal, \n  ChevronDown, Database, Sliders, Play, Info, Check, Clock, ExternalLink\n} from \"lucide-react\";\n\n// ==========================================\n// 1. SECURE PREVIEW NOTICE\n// ==========================================\nexport function SecurePreviewNotice({ className = \"\" }: { className?: string }) {\n  return (\n    <div className={`relative w-full overflow-hidden border-b border-amber-500/10 bg-amber-950/20 px-4 py-2 text-center backdrop-blur-sm ${className}`}>\n      <div className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,rgba(245,158,11,0.02),transparent_50%,rgba(245,158,11,0.02))]\" />\n      <div className=\"relative z-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-2.5 text-[11px] font-mono tracking-wider text-amber-400\">\n        <span className=\"relative flex h-2 w-2\">\n          <span className=\"animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-amber-400 opacity-75\"></span>\n          <span className=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-amber-500\"></span>\n        </span>\n        <span className=\"font-bold uppercase\">ZERO-TRUST SANDBOX ENCLAVE</span>\n        <span className=\"hidden md:inline text-white/30\">â€¢</span>\n        <span className=\"text-white/70\">Cryptographically isolated preview environment. State alterations are simulated local loops.</span>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 2. USER AVATAR\n// ==========================================\nexport interface UserProfile {\n  name: string;\n  email: string;\n  role: \"Client\" | \"Administrator\";\n  clearance: string;\n  avatarUrl?: string;\n}\n\nexport function UserAvatar({ \n  user, \n  showDetails = false \n}: { \n  user: UserProfile; \n  showDetails?: boolean;\n}) {\n  const [showCard, setShowCard] = useState(false);\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"relative\">\n      <button \n        onClick={() => setShowCard(!showCard)}\n        onKeyDown={(e) => {\n          if (e.key === 'Enter' || e.key === ' ') {\n            e.preventDefault();\n            setShowCard(!showCard);\n          }\n        }}\n        className=\"flex items-center gap-3 text-left focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#009DFF]/40 rounded-lg p-1.5 transition-colors hover:bg-white/[0.03] group cursor-pointer\"\n        aria-label=\"User profile settings\"\n        aria-expanded={showCard}\n      >\n        <div className=\"relative h-9 w-9 shrink-0 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-[12px] font-bold text-[#009DFF] group-hover:border-[#009DFF]/30 transition-all shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.05)]\">\n          {user.name.split(\" \").map(n => n[0]).join(\"\")}\n          <div className=\"absolute -bottom-0.5 -right-0.5 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full border border-[#050505] bg-emerald-500 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(16,185,129,0.6)]\" />\n        </div>\n        {showDetails && (\n          <div className=\"hidden md:block select-none\">\n            <div className=\"text-[12.5px] font-bold text-white leading-tight group-hover:text-[#009DFF] transition-colors\">{user.name}</div>\n            <div className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/45 mt-0.5\">{user.clearance}</div>\n          </div>\n        )}\n      </button>\n\n      <AnimatePresence>\n        {showCard && (\n          <>\n            <div className=\"fixed inset-0 z-40\" onClick={() => setShowCard(false)} />\n            <motion.div \n              initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 8, scale: 0.98 }}\n              animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0, scale: 1 }}\n              exit={{ opacity: 0, y: 8, scale: 0.98 }}\n              transition={{ duration: 0.15 }}\n              className=\"absolute right-0 bottom-full mb-2 lg:bottom-auto lg:top-full lg:mt-2 z-50 w-64 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#0a0a0a] p-4 shadow-[0_10px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)] backdrop-blur-md\"\n            >\n              <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n                <div className=\"text-[13px] font-bold text-white\">{user.name}</div>\n                <div className=\"text-[11px] text-white/50 font-mono mt-0.5\">{user.email}</div>\n                <div className=\"mt-2 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[9px] font-mono font-bold uppercase text-emerald-400\">\n                  {user.clearance}\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"py-2 space-y-1 text-[11.5px] font-mono\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center px-2 py-1.5 text-white/60\">\n                  <span>Authorized Role:</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{user.role}</span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center px-2 py-1.5 text-white/60\">\n                  <span>Node Latency:</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold\">14ms</span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center px-2 py-1.5 text-white/60\">\n                  <span>Enclave ID:</span>\n                  <span className=\"text-white/40\">GFF_0x7FFA</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"border-t border-white/5 pt-2 mt-1\">\n                <button \n                  onClick={() => setShowCard(false)}\n                  className=\"w-full flex items-center justify-between px-2 py-1.5 rounded text-left text-[11.5px] font-mono text-red-400 hover:bg-red-500/5 transition-colors cursor-pointer\"\n                >\n                  <span>Deauthorize Session</span>\n                  <LogOut className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                </button>\n              </div>\n            </motion.div>\n          </>\n        )}\n      </AnimatePresence>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 3. NOTIFICATION BELL\n// ==========================================\nexport interface SystemNotification {\n  id: string;\n  title: string;\n  desc: string;\n  severity: \"high\" | \"medium\" | \"low\";\n  timestamp: string;\n  unread: boolean;\n}\n\nexport function NotificationBell() {\n  const [showDropdown, setShowDropdown] = useState(false);\n  const [notifications, setNotifications] = useState<SystemNotification[]>([\n    {\n      id: \"1\",\n      title: \"eBPF System Alert\",\n      desc: \"RETAIL-CORE-A1 memory load exceeded 85% safety threshold.\",\n      severity: \"high\",\n      timestamp: \"2 mins ago\",\n      unread: true,\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"2\",\n      title: \"ISO-27001 Cryptographic Handshake\",\n      desc: \"Zero-trust tunnel session successfully signed.\",\n      severity: \"low\",\n      timestamp: \"15 mins ago\",\n      unread: true,\n    },\n    {\n      id: \"3\",\n      title: \"Ledger Settlement Complete\",\n      desc: \"Receipt GFF-2026-0899 cryptographically verified.\",\n      severity: \"medium\",\n      timestamp: \"2 hours ago\",\n      unread: false,\n    }\n  ]);\n\n  const unreadCount = notifications.filter(n => n.unread).length;\n\n  const markAllRead = () => {\n    setNotifications(notifications.map(n => ({ ...n, unread: false })));\n  };\n\n  const deleteNotification = (id: string, e: React.MouseEvent) => {\n    e.stopPropagation();\n    setNotifications(notifications.filter(n => n.id !== id));\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"relative\">\n      <button \n        onClick={() => setShowDropdown(!showDropdown)}\n        className=\"relative h-9 w-9 rounded-lg border border-white/5 hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/[0.03] flex items-center justify-center text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-all cursor-pointer focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#009DFF]/30\"\n        aria-label=\"System notifications\"\n        aria-expanded={showDropdown}\n      >\n        <Bell className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n        {unreadCount > 0 && (\n          <span className=\"absolute top-1.5 right-1.5 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[#E4000F] shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(228,0,15,0.6)]\" />\n        )}\n      </button>\n\n      <AnimatePresence>\n        {showDropdown && (\n          <>\n            <div className=\"fixed inset-0 z-40\" onClick={() => setShowDropdown(false)} />\n            <motion.div \n              initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 8, scale: 0.98 }}\n              animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0, scale: 1 }}\n              exit={{ opacity: 0, y: 8, scale: 0.98 }}\n              transition={{ duration: 0.15 }}\n              className=\"absolute right-0 top-full mt-2 z-50 w-80 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#0a0a0a]/95 p-4 shadow-[0_10px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)] backdrop-blur-md\"\n            >\n              <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center border-b border-white/5 pb-2.5 mb-2.5\">\n                <span className=\"text-[12px] font-mono font-bold text-white tracking-wider\">SYSTEM EVENTS</span>\n                {unreadCount > 0 && (\n                  <button \n                    onClick={markAllRead}\n                    className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] hover:underline cursor-pointer\"\n                  >\n                    Clear Badges\n                  </button>\n                )}\n              </div>\n\n              {notifications.length === 0 ? (\n                <div className=\"py-6 text-center text-[11px] font-mono text-white/30\">\n                  No active high-integrity events\n                </div>\n              ) : (\n                <div className=\"space-y-2 max-h-64 overflow-y-auto pr-1\">\n                  {notifications.map(notif => (\n                    <div \n                      key={notif.id}\n                      onClick={() => {\n                        setNotifications(notifications.map(n => n.id === notif.id ? { ...n, unread: false } : n));\n                      }}\n                      className={`relative p-2.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#020202]/50 hover:bg-[#020202]/85 hover:border-white/10 transition-all cursor-pointer ${notif.unread ? \"border-l-2 border-l-[#009DFF]\" : \"\"}`}\n                    >\n                      <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start gap-2\">\n                        <div className=\"flex gap-1.5 items-center\">\n                          {notif.severity === \"high\" && <AlertCircle className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#E4000F] shrink-0\" />}\n                          {notif.severity === \"medium\" && <Info className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 shrink-0\" />}\n                          {notif.severity === \"low\" && <CheckCircle className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-emerald-400 shrink-0\" />}\n                          <span className=\"text-[11.5px] font-bold text-white leading-tight\">{notif.title}</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <button \n                          onClick={(e) => deleteNotification(notif.id, e)}\n                          className=\"text-white/20 hover:text-white/60 text-[10px] p-0.5\"\n                        >\n                          <X className=\"w-3 h-3\" />\n                        </button>\n                      </div>\n                      <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 mt-1 font-mono leading-relaxed\">{notif.desc}</p>\n                      <div className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 font-mono mt-1.5 text-right\">{notif.timestamp}</div>\n                    </div>\n                  ))}\n                </div>\n              )}\n            </motion.div>\n          </>\n        )}\n      </AnimatePresence>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 4. ROLE SWITCHER PREVIEW\n// ==========================================\nexport function RoleSwitcherPreview({ \n  currentRole, \n  onRoleChange \n}: { \n  currentRole: \"Client\" | \"Administrator\";\n  onRoleChange: (role: \"Client\" | \"Administrator\") => void;\n}) {\n  const [switching, setSwitching] = useState(false);\n  const [scanStep, setScanStep] = useState(0);\n\n  const triggerSwitch = (role: \"Client\" | \"Administrator\") => {\n    if (role === currentRole) return;\n    setSwitching(true);\n    setScanStep(0);\n    const interval = setInterval(() => {\n      setScanStep(prev => {\n        if (prev < 3) return prev + 1;\n        return prev;\n      });\n    }, 350);\n\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      clearInterval(interval);\n      setSwitching(false);\n      onRoleChange(role);\n    }, 1400);\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"relative\">\n      <div className=\"inline-flex rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-black/40 p-0.5\">\n        <button \n          onClick={() => triggerSwitch(\"Client\")}\n          disabled={switching}\n          className={`px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-[10.5px] font-mono tracking-wider transition-all cursor-pointer ${currentRole === \"Client\" ? \"bg-white/10 text-white font-bold\" : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white/75\"}`}\n        >\n          CLIENT\n        </button>\n        <button \n          onClick={() => triggerSwitch(\"Administrator\")}\n          disabled={switching}\n          className={`px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-[10.5px] font-mono tracking-wider transition-all cursor-pointer ${currentRole === \"Administrator\" ? \"bg-white/10 text-white font-bold\" : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white/75\"}`}\n        >\n          ADMIN\n        </button>\n      </div>\n\n      <AnimatePresence>\n        {switching && (\n          <motion.div \n            initial={{ opacity: 0 }}\n            animate={{ opacity: 1 }}\n            exit={{ opacity: 0 }}\n            className=\"fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center bg-black/80 backdrop-blur-md\"\n          >\n            <div className=\"w-80 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-[#080808] text-center shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(0,157,255,0.1)] relative overflow-hidden\">\n              <div className=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#009DFF] via-purple-500 to-[#E4000F]\" />\n              <div className=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-[#009DFF] animate-spin\">\n                <RefreshCw className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n              </div>\n              <h4 className=\"text-[14px] font-bold font-mono tracking-widest text-white uppercase\">RENEGOTIATING COMPLIANCE KEY</h4>\n              <p className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/45 mt-2\">Isolating local thread stack and validating clearances...</p>\n              \n              <div className=\"mt-4 border border-white/5 rounded-lg p-2.5 bg-black/50 text-left font-mono text-[10px] space-y-1\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  <Check className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-emerald-400\" />\n                  <span className={scanStep >= 0 ? \"text-emerald-400\" : \"text-white/30\"}>Resetting core local memory stack</span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  {scanStep >= 1 ? <Check className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-emerald-400\" /> : <div className=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] animate-ping mx-1\" />}\n                  <span className={scanStep >= 1 ? \"text-emerald-400\" : \"text-white/30\"}>Exchanging GFF_SHA256_PRIVATE_KEY</span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  {scanStep >= 2 ? <Check className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-emerald-400\" /> : <div className=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] mx-1\" />}\n                  <span className={scanStep >= 2 ? \"text-emerald-400\" : \"text-white/30\"}>Compiling role permissions</span>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </motion.div>\n        )}\n      </AnimatePresence>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 5. WORKSPACE BREADCRUMBS\n// ==========================================\nexport interface BreadcrumbItem {\n  label: string;\n  href?: string;\n}\n\nexport function WorkspaceBreadcrumbs({ \n  items \n}: { \n  items: BreadcrumbItem[];\n}) {\n  return (\n    <nav className=\"flex items-center space-x-2 text-[11px] font-mono text-white/40 select-none\">\n      <Link href=\"/portal\" className=\"hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-1\">\n        <Shield className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n        <span>GFF CORE</span>\n      </Link>\n      {items.map((item, index) => (\n        <React.Fragment key={index}>\n          <ChevronRight className=\"w-3 h-3 text-white/20 shrink-0\" />\n          {item.href ? (\n            <Link href={item.href} className=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">\n              {item.label.toUpperCase()}\n            </Link>\n          ) : (\n            <span className=\"text-white font-bold tracking-wider\">{item.label.toUpperCase()}</span>\n          )}\n        </React.Fragment>\n      ))}\n    </nav>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 6. WORKSPACE COMMAND BUTTON (with working Palette)\n// ==========================================\nexport function WorkspaceCommandButton({ \n  onClick \n}: { \n  onClick: () => void;\n}) {\n  const isMac = typeof window !== \"undefined\" && window.navigator.platform.toUpperCase().indexOf(\"MAC\") >= 0;\n\n  return (\n    <button \n      onClick={onClick}\n      className=\"flex h-9 w-full md:w-56 items-center justify-between rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] px-3 text-left hover:border-white/15 hover:bg-white/[0.04] transition-all cursor-pointer focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#009DFF]/30 group\"\n    >\n      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-white/40 group-hover:text-white/60 transition-colors\">\n        <Search className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n        <span className=\"text-[11.5px] font-mono tracking-wider\">SECURE SEARCH...</span>\n      </div>\n      <kbd className=\"hidden md:inline-flex h-5 select-none items-center gap-0.5 rounded border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-1.5 font-mono text-[9px] font-medium text-white/30\">\n        {isMac ? \"âŒ˜\" : \"Ctrl+\"}K\n      </kbd>\n    </button>\n  );\n}\n\n// THE ACTUAL WORKING COMMAND PALETTE\nexport function CommandPalette({ \n  isOpen, \n  onClose,\n  onNavigate\n}: { \n  isOpen: boolean; \n  onClose: () => void;\n  onNavigate?: (tab: string) => void;\n}) {\n  const [search, setSearch] = useState(\"\");\n  const inputRef = useRef<HTMLInputElement>(null);\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (isOpen) {\n      setTimeout(() => inputRef.current?.focus(), 50);\n      document.body.style.overflow = \"hidden\";\n    } else {\n      document.body.style.overflow = \"\";\n    }\n    return () => {\n      document.body.style.overflow = \"\";\n    };\n  }, [isOpen]);\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const handleKeyDown = (e: KeyboardEvent) => {\n      if (e.key === \"k\" && (e.metaKey || e.ctrlKey)) {\n        e.preventDefault();\n        isOpen ? onClose() : void 0; // Handled in host, but good defensive code\n      }\n      if (e.key === \"Escape\" && isOpen) {\n        onClose();\n      }\n    };\n    window.addEventListener(\"keydown\", handleKeyDown);\n    return () => window.removeEventListener(\"keydown\", handleKeyDown);\n  }, [isOpen, onClose]);\n\n  const items = [\n    { category: \"DIAGNOSTICS\", label: \"Inspect Agent Health Stack\", shortcut: \"H\", tab: \"agent_health\" },\n    { category: \"DIAGNOSTICS\", label: \"Live Thread CPU Metrics\", shortcut: \"M\", tab: \"agent_health\" },\n    { category: \"OPERATIONS\", label: \"Continuous Delivery Pipeline\", shortcut: \"D\", tab: \"delivery\" },\n    { category: \"OPERATIONS\", label: \"Integration Node Endpoint map\", shortcut: \"E\", tab: \"adoption\" },\n    { category: \"FINANCIALS\", label: \"Cryptographic Invoice Ledger\", shortcut: \"I\", tab: \"spend\" },\n    { category: \"FINANCIALS\", label: \"Compute and Token Spend parameters\", shortcut: \"S\", tab: \"spend\" },\n    { category: \"COMPLIANCE\", label: \"ISO-27001 Audit checklist\", shortcut: \"G\", tab: \"governance\" },\n    { category: \"COMPLIANCE\", label: \"Recent eBPF Guardrail Violations\", shortcut: \"V\", tab: \"governance\" },\n    { category: \"SUPPORT\", label: \"Open Secure Messaging Terminal\", shortcut: \"T\", tab: \"support\" }\n  ];\n\n  const filtered = items.filter(item => \n    item.label.toLowerCase().includes(search.toLowerCase()) || \n    item.category.toLowerCase().includes(search.toLowerCase())\n  );\n\n  if (!isOpen) return null;\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"fixed inset-0 z-[999] flex items-start justify-center bg-black/80 p-4 pt-[10vh] backdrop-blur-md\">\n      <div className=\"fixed inset-0\" onClick={onClose} />\n      <div className=\"relative w-full max-w-xl rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-[#080808]/95 p-4 shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.9)] backdrop-blur-md\">\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3 border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n          <Search className=\"w-4 h-4 text-white/40 shrink-0\" />\n          <input \n            ref={inputRef}\n            type=\"text\"\n            value={search}\n            onChange={(e) => setSearch(e.target.value)}\n            placeholder=\"Type a command or module name...\"\n            className=\"w-full bg-transparent text-[13.5px] font-mono text-white placeholder-white/35 outline-none\"\n          />\n          <button \n            onClick={onClose}\n            className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 border border-white/10 rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 hover:bg-white/5 transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n          >\n            ESC\n          </button>\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"mt-3 max-h-72 overflow-y-auto pr-1\">\n          {filtered.length === 0 ? (\n            <div className=\"py-6 text-center text-[12px] font-mono text-white/30\">\n              No results found matching &ldquo;{search}&rdquo;\n            </div>\n          ) : (\n            <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n              {[\"DIAGNOSTICS\", \"OPERATIONS\", \"FINANCIALS\", \"COMPLIANCE\", \"SUPPORT\"].map(cat => {\n                const catItems = filtered.filter(i => i.category === cat);\n                if (catItems.length === 0) return null;\n                return (\n                  <div key={cat} className=\"space-y-1\">\n                    <div className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold tracking-widest text-white/25 px-2\">{cat}</div>\n                    {catItems.map((item, idx) => (\n                      <button \n                        key={idx}\n                        onClick={() => {\n                          if (onNavigate) onNavigate(item.tab);\n                          onClose();\n                        }}\n                        className=\"w-full flex justify-between items-center px-2 py-1.5 rounded-lg text-left text-[12px] font-mono text-white/70 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/[0.04] transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n                      >\n                        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                          <Terminal className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#009DFF]/70\" />\n                          <span>{item.label}</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <kbd className=\"h-5 select-none items-center gap-0.5 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] px-1.5 text-[9px] text-white/30\">\n                          {item.shortcut}\n                        </kbd>\n                      </button>\n                    ))}\n                  </div>\n                );\n              })}\n            </div>\n          )}\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 7. WORKSPACE CARD (with Spotlight effect)\n// ==========================================\nexport function WorkspaceCard({ \n  children, \n  className = \"\",\n  spotlightColor = \"rgba(0,157,255,0.05)\"\n}: { \n  children: React.ReactNode; \n  className?: string;\n  spotlightColor?: string;\n}) {\n  const divRef = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null);\n  const [position, setPosition] = useState({ x: 0, y: 0 });\n  const [opacity, setOpacity] = useState(0);\n\n  const handleMouseMove = (e: React.MouseEvent<HTMLDivElement>) => {\n    if (!divRef.current) return;\n    const div = divRef.current;\n    const rect = div.getBoundingClientRect();\n    setPosition({ x: e.clientX - rect.left, y: e.clientY - rect.top });\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <div \n      ref={divRef}\n      onMouseMove={handleMouseMove}\n      onMouseEnter={() => setOpacity(1)}\n      onMouseLeave={() => setOpacity(0)}\n      className={`relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/30 backdrop-blur-sm p-5 transition-all hover:border-white/10 ${className}`}\n    >\n      <div \n        className=\"pointer-events-none absolute -inset-px rounded-2xl opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300\"\n        style={{\n          opacity,\n          background: `radial-gradient(350px circle at ${position.x}px ${position.y}px, ${spotlightColor}, transparent 80%)`\n        }}\n      />\n      <div className=\"relative z-10\">{children}</div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 8. METRIC TILE (with Live animated Sparkline)\n// ==========================================\nexport function MetricTile({ \n  title, \n  value, \n  delta, \n  direction, \n  status = \"stable\", \n  sparkPoints = [30, 40, 35, 50, 45, 60, 55, 70, 65, 80]\n}: { \n  title: string; \n  value: string; \n  delta: string; \n  direction: \"up\" | \"down\" | \"neutral\"; \n  status?: \"normal\" | \"warning\" | \"error\" | \"stable\";\n  sparkPoints?: number[];\n}) {\n  // Build SVG path for sparkline\n  const width = 120;\n  const height = 40;\n  const maxVal = Math.max(...sparkPoints);\n  const minVal = Math.min(...sparkPoints);\n  const range = maxVal - minVal || 1;\n\n  const points = sparkPoints.map((val, idx) => {\n    const x = (idx / (sparkPoints.length - 1)) * width;\n    const y = height - ((val - minVal) / range) * (height - 8) - 4;\n    return `${x},${y}`;\n  }).join(\" \");\n\n  const deltaColor = direction === \"up\" ? \"text-emerald-400\" : direction === \"down\" ? \"text-[#E4000F]\" : \"text-white/40\";\n  const strokeColor = direction === \"up\" ? \"#10b981\" : direction === \"down\" ? \"#E4000F\" : \"#009DFF\";\n\n  return (\n    <WorkspaceCard className=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-4\">\n      <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n        <span className=\"text-[10.5px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">{title}</span>\n        <div className=\"text-[22px] font-bold tracking-tight text-white\">{value}</div>\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-mono leading-none\">\n          <span className={`font-bold ${deltaColor}`}>\n            {direction === \"up\" ? \"+\" : \"\"}{delta}\n          </span>\n          <span className=\"text-white/20\">â€¢</span>\n          <span className=\"text-white/40 uppercase text-[9.5px]\">vs last cycle</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"flex flex-col items-end shrink-0 select-none\">\n        <svg width={width} height={height} className=\"overflow-visible\">\n          <polyline \n            fill=\"none\" \n            stroke={strokeColor} \n            strokeWidth=\"1.5\" \n            points={points} \n            strokeLinecap=\"round\"\n            strokeLinejoin=\"round\"\n            className=\"transition-all duration-500\"\n          />\n          {/* Subtle glow on path */}\n          <polyline \n            fill=\"none\" \n            stroke={strokeColor} \n            strokeWidth=\"4\" \n            points={points} \n            strokeLinecap=\"round\"\n            strokeLinejoin=\"round\"\n            className=\"opacity-15 blur-sm transition-all duration-500\"\n          />\n        </svg>\n        <div className=\"mt-1 flex items-center gap-1\">\n          <span className={`h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full ${\n            status === \"normal\" ? \"bg-emerald-500\" :\n            status === \"warning\" ? \"bg-amber-400\" :\n            status === \"error\" ? \"bg-[#E4000F]\" : \"bg-[#009DFF]\"\n          }`} />\n          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest\">{status}</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </WorkspaceCard>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 9. STATUS BADGE\n// ==========================================\nexport type BadgeState = \"active\" | \"warning\" | \"error\" | \"stable\" | \"decoupled\";\n\nexport function StatusBadge({ \n  state, \n  label \n}: { \n  state: BadgeState; \n  label: string;\n}) {\n  const styles = {\n    active: \"bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 border-emerald-500/25\",\n    warning: \"bg-amber-400/10 text-amber-400 border-amber-400/25\",\n    error: \"bg-red-500/10 text-red-400 border-red-500/25\",\n    stable: \"bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF] border-[#009DFF]/25\",\n    decoupled: \"bg-white/5 text-white/50 border-white/10\"\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <span className={`inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-mono font-bold uppercase border ${styles[state]}`}>\n      {state === \"active\" && (\n        <span className=\"relative flex h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0\">\n          <span className=\"animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-emerald-400 opacity-75\"></span>\n          <span className=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full h-1.5 w-1.5 bg-emerald-500\"></span>\n        </span>\n      )}\n      <span>{label}</span>\n    </span>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 10. DATA TABLE\n// ==========================================\nexport interface TableColumn<T> {\n  key: keyof T | string;\n  header: string;\n  render?: (row: T) => React.ReactNode;\n  sortable?: boolean;\n}\n\nexport function DataTable<T extends { id: string | number }>({ \n  columns, \n  data, \n  pageSize = 5,\n  onRowClick\n}: { \n  columns: TableColumn<T>[]; \n  data: T[]; \n  pageSize?: number;\n  onRowClick?: (row: T) => void;\n}) {\n  const [currentPage, setCurrentPage] = useState(1);\n  const [sortKey, setSortKey] = useState<keyof T | string | null>(null);\n  const [sortOrder, setSortOrder] = useState<\"asc\" | \"desc\">(\"asc\");\n\n  const totalPages = Math.ceil(data.length / pageSize) || 1;\n\n  const handleSort = (key: keyof T | string, sortable?: boolean) => {\n    if (!sortable) return;\n    if (sortKey === key) {\n      setSortOrder(sortOrder === \"asc\" ? \"desc\" : \"asc\");\n    } else {\n      setSortKey(key);\n      setSortOrder(\"asc\");\n    }\n  };\n\n  // Sort and paginate\n  let processedData = [...data];\n  if (sortKey) {\n    processedData.sort((a, b) => {\n      const aVal = a[sortKey as keyof T];\n      const bVal = b[sortKey as keyof T];\n      if (typeof aVal === \"string\" && typeof bVal === \"string\") {\n        return sortOrder === \"asc\" ? aVal.localeCompare(bVal) : bVal.localeCompare(aVal);\n      }\n      return sortOrder === \"asc\" \n        ? (aVal > bVal ? 1 : -1)\n        : (aVal < bVal ? 1 : -1);\n    });\n  }\n\n  const paginatedData = processedData.slice(\n    (currentPage - 1) * pageSize,\n    currentPage * pageSize\n  );\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-sm\">\n      <div className=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n        <table className=\"w-full text-left font-mono text-[11.5px] text-white/70\">\n          <thead>\n            <tr className=\"bg-white/[0.02] border-b border-white/5 text-white/40 text-[9.5px] uppercase select-none\">\n              {columns.map((col, idx) => (\n                <th \n                  key={idx} \n                  onClick={() => handleSort(col.key, col.sortable)}\n                  className={`p-4 font-bold tracking-wider ${col.sortable ? \"hover:text-white cursor-pointer\" : \"\"}`}\n                >\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1\">\n                    <span>{col.header}</span>\n                    {col.sortable && sortKey === col.key && (\n                      <span className=\"text-[9px] text-[#009DFF]\">{sortOrder === \"asc\" ? \"â–²\" : \"â–¼\"}</span>\n                    )}\n                  </div>\n                </th>\n              ))}\n            </tr>\n          </thead>\n          <tbody className=\"divide-y divide-white/5\">\n            {paginatedData.length === 0 ? (\n              <tr>\n                <td colSpan={columns.length} className=\"p-8 text-center text-[11px] text-white/35\">\n                  No core records match current queries.\n                </td>\n              </tr>\n            ) : (\n              paginatedData.map((row, rIdx) => (\n                <tr \n                  key={row.id || rIdx} \n                  onClick={() => onRowClick?.(row)}\n                  className={`transition-colors ${onRowClick ? \"hover:bg-white/[0.02] cursor-pointer\" : \"hover:bg-white/[0.005]\"}`}\n                >\n                  {columns.map((col, cIdx) => (\n                    <td key={cIdx} className=\"p-4 leading-normal\">\n                      {col.render ? col.render(row) : (row[col.key as keyof T] as React.ReactNode)}\n                    </td>\n                  ))}\n                </tr>\n              ))\n            )}\n          </tbody>\n        </table>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Pagination strip */}\n      {totalPages > 1 && (\n        <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center bg-white/[0.01] border-t border-white/5 p-4 select-none\">\n          <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/35\">\n            PAGE {currentPage} OF {totalPages} ({data.length} RECORDS)\n          </span>\n          <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n            <button \n              disabled={currentPage === 1}\n              onClick={() => setCurrentPage(p => Math.max(1, p - 1))}\n              className=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded border border-white/5 text-[10px] text-white font-mono hover:bg-white/5 disabled:opacity-25 transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n            >\n              PREVIOUS\n            </button>\n            <button \n              disabled={currentPage === totalPages}\n              onClick={() => setCurrentPage(p => Math.min(totalPages, p + 1))}\n              className=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded border border-white/5 text-[10px] text-white font-mono hover:bg-white/5 disabled:opacity-25 transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n            >\n              NEXT\n            </button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 11. FILTER BAR\n// ==========================================\nexport function FilterBar({ \n  searchPlaceholder = \"Filter records...\",\n  onSearchChange,\n  categories = [],\n  onCategoryChange,\n  selectedCategory = \"\"\n}: { \n  searchPlaceholder?: string;\n  onSearchChange: (val: string) => void;\n  categories?: string[];\n  onCategoryChange?: (val: string) => void;\n  selectedCategory?: string;\n}) {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 items-stretch\">\n      <div className=\"relative flex-grow\">\n        <Search className=\"absolute left-3 top-2.5 w-4 h-4 text-white/30\" />\n        <input \n          type=\"text\"\n          onChange={(e) => onSearchChange(e.target.value)}\n          placeholder={searchPlaceholder}\n          className=\"w-full h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] pl-9 pr-4 text-[12px] font-mono text-white placeholder-white/30 outline-none focus:border-white/15 focus:bg-white/[0.04] transition-all\"\n        />\n      </div>\n\n      {categories.length > 0 && onCategoryChange && (\n        <div className=\"relative shrink-0\">\n          <select \n            value={selectedCategory}\n            onChange={(e) => onCategoryChange(e.target.value)}\n            className=\"h-9 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:bg-white/[0.04] px-3 pr-8 text-[12px] font-mono text-white/70 focus:text-white outline-none transition-all cursor-pointer appearance-none\"\n          >\n            <option value=\"\" className=\"bg-[#0c0c0c] text-white\">ALL CATEGORIES</option>\n            {categories.map((cat, idx) => (\n              <option key={idx} value={cat} className=\"bg-[#0c0c0c] text-white\">{cat.toUpperCase()}</option>\n            ))}\n          </select>\n          <ChevronDown className=\"absolute right-3 top-2.5 w-4 h-4 text-white/40 pointer-events-none\" />\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 12. EMPTY STATE\n// ==========================================\nexport function EmptyState({ \n  title, \n  desc, \n  actionLabel, \n  onAction \n}: { \n  title: string; \n  desc: string; \n  actionLabel?: string; \n  onAction?: () => void;\n}) {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"text-center py-12 px-4 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 border-dashed bg-white/[0.005] select-none\">\n      <div className=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-full border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-[#009DFF]/60 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.03)]\">\n        <Terminal className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n      </div>\n      <h4 className=\"text-[14px] font-bold text-white font-mono tracking-wider\">{title.toUpperCase()}</h4>\n      <p className=\"text-[11.5px] font-mono text-white/45 max-w-sm mx-auto mt-2 leading-relaxed\">{desc}</p>\n      {actionLabel && onAction && (\n        <button \n          onClick={onAction}\n          className=\"mt-5 inline-flex h-8 px-4 rounded bg-[#009DFF] hover:bg-[#0082d4] text-white font-mono font-bold text-[10.5px] uppercase tracking-wider items-center gap-1.5 transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n        >\n          <span>{actionLabel}</span>\n          <ArrowRight className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n        </button>\n      )}\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 13. ACTIVITY FEED\n// ==========================================\nexport interface ActivityItem {\n  id: string;\n  category: \"security\" | \"compile\" | \"ledger\" | \"health\";\n  title: string;\n  desc: string;\n  timestamp: string;\n  meta?: string;\n}\n\nexport function ActivityFeed({ \n  items \n}: { \n  items: ActivityItem[];\n}) {\n  const getIcon = (cat: string) => {\n    switch (cat) {\n      case \"security\": return <Lock className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#009DFF]\" />;\n      case \"compile\": return <Cpu className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-indigo-400\" />;\n      case \"ledger\": return <FileText className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-emerald-400\" />;\n      default: return <Activity className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400\" />;\n    }\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"space-y-3.5\">\n      {items.map((item) => (\n        <div key={item.id} className=\"flex gap-3 items-start group\">\n          <div className=\"p-1.5 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] mt-0.5 shrink-0 group-hover:border-white/15 transition-all\">\n            {getIcon(item.category)}\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"flex-grow pb-3.5 border-b border-white/5 last:border-0\">\n            <div className=\"flex flex-wrap justify-between items-baseline gap-2 select-none\">\n              <span className=\"text-[12px] font-bold text-white group-hover:text-[#009DFF] transition-colors\">{item.title}</span>\n              <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/35\">{item.timestamp}</span>\n            </div>\n            <p className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/50 mt-1 leading-relaxed\">{item.desc}</p>\n            {item.meta && (\n              <span className=\"mt-1.5 inline-block text-[9.5px] font-mono text-white/30 bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5 rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 select-none\">\n                HASH: {item.meta}\n              </span>\n            )}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      ))}\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 14. TIMELINE\n// ==========================================\nexport interface TimelineStep {\n  title: string;\n  desc: string;\n  status: \"complete\" | \"current\" | \"pending\";\n  timestamp?: string;\n}\n\nexport function Timeline({ \n  steps \n}: { \n  steps: TimelineStep[];\n}) {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"space-y-6 relative before:absolute before:left-[11px] before:top-2 before:bottom-2 before:w-0.5 before:bg-white/5 select-none\">\n      {steps.map((step, idx) => (\n        <div key={idx} className=\"flex gap-4 relative\">\n          <div className=\"relative z-10 shrink-0\">\n            {step.status === \"complete\" && (\n              <div className=\"h-6 w-6 rounded-full border border-emerald-500/30 bg-emerald-950/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(16,185,129,0.2)]\">\n                <Check className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n              </div>\n            )}\n            {step.status === \"current\" && (\n              <div className=\"h-6 w-6 rounded-full border border-[#009DFF]/30 bg-[#009DFF]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#009DFF] shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(0,157,255,0.2)] animate-pulse\">\n                <Clock className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n              </div>\n            )}\n            {step.status === \"pending\" && (\n              <div className=\"h-6 w-6 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.01] flex items-center justify-center text-white/20\">\n                <div className=\"h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-white/10\" />\n              </div>\n            )}\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"flex-grow pt-0.5\">\n            <div className=\"flex justify-between items-baseline gap-2\">\n              <h5 className={`text-[12.5px] font-mono font-bold ${step.status === \"complete\" ? \"text-white\" : step.status === \"current\" ? \"text-[#009DFF]\" : \"text-white/40\"}`}>\n                {step.title.toUpperCase()}\n              </h5>\n              {step.timestamp && (\n                <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-white/30\">{step.timestamp}</span>\n              )}\n            </div>\n            <p className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/45 mt-1 leading-relaxed max-w-lg\">{step.desc}</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      ))}\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 15. DOCUMENT CARD\n// ==========================================\nexport function DocumentCard({ \n  title, \n  fileSize, \n  type = \"PDF\", \n  sha256,\n  onDownload \n}: { \n  title: string; \n  fileSize: string; \n  type?: string; \n  sha256: string;\n  onDownload?: () => void;\n}) {\n  const [downloading, setDownloading] = useState(false);\n\n  const handleDownload = () => {\n    if (!onDownload) return;\n    setDownloading(true);\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setDownloading(false);\n      onDownload();\n    }, 1200);\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <WorkspaceCard className=\"flex flex-col h-full justify-between\">\n      <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n        <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start select-none\">\n          <div className=\"p-2 rounded bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-400\">\n            <FileText className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n          </div>\n          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-white/30 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded px-1.5 py-0.5\">\n            {type}\n          </span>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h4 className=\"text-[13px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight leading-snug\">{title}</h4>\n          <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/35 mt-1 block select-none\">FILE SIZE: {fileSize}</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"border-t border-white/5 pt-3.5 mt-4 space-y-3 font-mono\">\n        <div className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/30 select-none\">\n          <span className=\"font-bold text-white/50 block mb-0.5\">SHA-256 SUM:</span>\n          <span className=\"truncate block font-mono text-[9px] text-[#009DFF]/60\">{sha256}</span>\n        </div>\n\n        <button \n          onClick={handleDownload}\n          disabled={downloading}\n          className=\"w-full inline-flex h-8 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 rounded border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.01] text-[10.5px] font-bold text-white hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:border-white/25 transition-all disabled:opacity-50 cursor-pointer select-none\"\n        >\n          {downloading ? (\n            <>\n              <RefreshCw className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 animate-spin\" />\n              <span>PULLING FILE...</span>\n            </>\n          ) : (\n            <>\n              <Download className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n              <span>DOWNLOAD RECOGNIZED</span>\n            </>\n          )}\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </WorkspaceCard>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 16. INVOICE CARD\n// ==========================================\nexport function InvoiceCard({ \n  invoiceNo, \n  issueDate, \n  amount, \n  status = \"verified\",\n  signature \n}: { \n  invoiceNo: string; \n  issueDate: string; \n  amount: string; \n  status?: \"verified\" | \"settled\" | \"pending\";\n  signature: string;\n}) {\n  const [verifying, setVerifying] = useState(false);\n  const [sigOk, setSigOk] = useState(true);\n\n  const triggerVerification = () => {\n    setVerifying(true);\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setVerifying(false);\n      setSigOk(true);\n    }, 1500);\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <WorkspaceCard className=\"space-y-4 font-mono text-[11.5px]\">\n      <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start border-b border-white/5 pb-3 select-none\">\n        <div>\n          <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/35 block uppercase font-mono\">Ledger Ledger Reference</span>\n          <span className=\"text-[12.5px] font-bold text-white mt-0.5 block\">{invoiceNo}</span>\n        </div>\n        <StatusBadge \n          state={status === \"verified\" || status === \"settled\" ? \"active\" : \"warning\"} \n          label={status} \n        />\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"space-y-2 select-none\">\n        <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n          <span className=\"text-white/40\">Timestamp Block:</span>\n          <span className=\"text-white/70\">{issueDate}</span>\n        </div>\n        <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n          <span className=\"text-white/40\">Amount Settled:</span>\n          <span className=\"text-white font-bold text-[#009DFF]\">{amount}</span>\n        </div>\n        <div className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/30 pt-1 border-t border-white/5 mt-1.5\">\n          <span className=\"block font-bold text-white/50 mb-0.5\">CRYPTOGRAPHIC SIGNATURE:</span>\n          <span className=\"truncate block text-[9px] text-[#00FFC2]/75\">{signature}</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <button \n        onClick={triggerVerification}\n        disabled={verifying}\n        className=\"w-full inline-flex h-8 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 rounded border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.01] text-[10.5px] font-bold text-white hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:border-white/25 transition-all disabled:opacity-50 cursor-pointer select-none\"\n      >\n        {verifying ? (\n          <>\n            <RefreshCw className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 animate-spin text-[#00FFC2]\" />\n            <span>EXCHANGING SEALS...</span>\n          </>\n        ) : sigOk ? (\n          <>\n            <ShieldCheck className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#00FFC2]\" />\n            <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2]/90\">CRYPTO SEAL VALID</span>\n          </>\n        ) : (\n          <span>VALIDATE COVENANT</span>\n        )}\n      </button>\n    </WorkspaceCard>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 17. SUPPORT TICKET CARD\n// ==========================================\nexport function SupportTicketCard({ \n  ticketId, \n  subject, \n  slaTimer, \n  priority = \"P1\", \n  status = \"OPEN\" \n}: { \n  ticketId: string; \n  subject: string; \n  slaTimer: string; \n  priority?: \"P1\" | \"P2\" | \"P3\";\n  status?: string;\n}) {\n  return (\n    <WorkspaceCard className=\"space-y-4 font-mono text-[11.5px]\">\n      <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start select-none\">\n        <div>\n          <span className=\"text-[9.5px] text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/10 border border-[#009DFF]/20 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-bold\">\n            {ticketId}\n          </span>\n          <span className=\"ml-2 text-[9.5px] text-red-400 bg-red-400/10 border border-red-400/20 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded font-bold\">\n            {priority} SLA\n          </span>\n        </div>\n        <span className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/35 uppercase tracking-widest\">{status}</span>\n      </div>\n\n      <div>\n        <h5 className=\"text-[12.5px] font-bold text-white leading-snug\">{subject}</h5>\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"border-t border-white/5 pt-3.5 flex justify-between items-center select-none\">\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-white/40\">\n          <Clock className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-amber-400 animate-pulse\" />\n          <span>SLA EXPIRES IN:</span>\n        </div>\n        <span className=\"text-white font-bold font-mono text-[12px] text-amber-400\">{slaTimer}</span>\n      </div>\n\n      <button className=\"w-full inline-flex h-8 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 rounded border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.01] text-[10.5px] font-bold text-white hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:border-white/25 transition-all cursor-pointer select-none\">\n        <MessageSquare className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n        <span>LAUNCH SECURE WIRE</span>\n      </button>\n    </WorkspaceCard>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 18. ANALYTICS PANEL (with Live telemetry curves)\n// ==========================================\nexport function AnalyticsPanel() {\n  const [computeUsage, setComputeUsage] = useState<number[]>([32, 45, 38, 52, 48, 65, 58, 72, 69, 85, 78, 82]);\n  \n  useEffect(() => {\n    const timer = setInterval(() => {\n      setComputeUsage(prev => {\n        const nextVal = Math.min(100, Math.max(10, prev[prev.length - 1] + (Math.floor(Math.random() * 12) - 6)));\n        return [...prev.slice(1), nextVal];\n      });\n    }, 2000);\n    return () => clearInterval(timer);\n  }, []);\n\n  const width = 600;\n  const height = 180;\n  const max = Math.max(...computeUsage);\n  const min = Math.min(...computeUsage);\n  const range = max - min || 1;\n\n  const areaPoints = [\n    `0,${height}`,\n    ...computeUsage.map((val, idx) => {\n      const x = (idx / (computeUsage.length - 1)) * width;\n      const y = height - ((val - min) / range) * (height - 24) - 12;\n      return `${x},${y}`;\n    }),\n    `${width},${height}`\n  ].join(\" \");\n\n  const linePoints = computeUsage.map((val, idx) => {\n    const x = (idx / (computeUsage.length - 1)) * width;\n    const y = height - ((val - min) / range) * (height - 24) - 12;\n    return `${x},${y}`;\n  }).join(\" \");\n\n  return (\n    <WorkspaceCard className=\"space-y-5\">\n      <div className=\"flex flex-wrap justify-between items-start gap-4 select-none\">\n        <div>\n          <h4 className=\"text-[14px] font-bold text-white font-mono tracking-wider uppercase\">Enclave Computing Matrix</h4>\n          <p className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/45 mt-1\">Sovereign thread capacity and memory boundaries over active epoch.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div className=\"flex gap-4 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n          <div>\n            <span className=\"text-white/30 block text-[9.5px] uppercase\">Peak Load</span>\n            <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{max}%</span>\n          </div>\n          <div>\n            <span className=\"text-white/30 block text-[9.5px] uppercase\">Base Load</span>\n            <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{min}%</span>\n          </div>\n          <div>\n            <span className=\"text-white/30 block text-[9.5px] uppercase\">State Cache</span>\n            <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold\">100% SECURE</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* SVG graph */}\n      <div className=\"relative w-full overflow-hidden select-none\">\n        <svg viewBox={`0 0 ${width} ${height}`} className=\"w-full h-auto overflow-visible\" preserveAspectRatio=\"none\">\n          {/* Grids */}\n          {[0.25, 0.5, 0.75].map((pct, idx) => (\n            <line \n              key={idx}\n              x1=\"0\" y1={height * pct} x2={width} y2={height * pct}\n              stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.03)\"\n              strokeWidth=\"1\"\n              strokeDasharray=\"4 4\"\n            />\n          ))}\n          {/* Area fill */}\n          <polygon \n            fill=\"url(#sparkGradient)\" \n            points={areaPoints} \n            className=\"transition-all duration-500\"\n          />\n          {/* Path line */}\n          <polyline \n            fill=\"none\" \n            stroke=\"#009DFF\" \n            strokeWidth=\"2\" \n            points={linePoints} \n            strokeLinecap=\"round\"\n            strokeLinejoin=\"round\"\n            className=\"transition-all duration-500\"\n          />\n          <polyline \n            fill=\"none\" \n            stroke=\"#009DFF\" \n            strokeWidth=\"6\" \n            points={linePoints} \n            strokeLinecap=\"round\"\n            strokeLinejoin=\"round\"\n            className=\"opacity-15 blur-sm transition-all duration-500\"\n          />\n\n          <defs>\n            <linearGradient id=\"sparkGradient\" x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"0\" y2=\"1\">\n              <stop offset=\"0%\" stopColor=\"#009DFF\" stopOpacity=\"0.15\" />\n              <stop offset=\"100%\" stopColor=\"#009DFF\" stopOpacity=\"0.00\" />\n            </linearGradient>\n          </defs>\n        </svg>\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 pt-2 border-t border-white/5 select-none\">\n        <span>EPOCH ACTIVE: 14:22:00 -> PRESENT</span>\n        <span>TELEMETRY POLLING INTERVAL: 2000MS</span>\n      </div>\n    </WorkspaceCard>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 19. GOVERNANCE PANEL\n// ==========================================\nexport interface ComplianceRule {\n  id: string;\n  name: string;\n  status: \"verified\" | \"warning\";\n  desc: string;\n}\n\nexport function GovernancePanel() {\n  const [rules, setRules] = useState<ComplianceRule[]>([\n    { id: \"1\", name: \"ISO-27001 Enclave Isolation\", status: \"verified\", desc: \"Local hardware memory boundaries isolated completely in sandbox.\" },\n    { id: \"2\", name: \"eBPF Event Log Streaming\", status: \"verified\", desc: \"Continuous kernel security auditing streams registered with zero gaps.\" },\n    { id: \"3\", name: \"SOC2 Administrative Decoupling\", status: \"verified\", desc: \"No core platform access routes exist inside user enclaves.\" },\n    { id: \"4\", name: \"Regulatory Compliance Ledger Check\", status: \"verified\", desc: \"No guardrail boundaries triggered violations during this epoch.\" }\n  ]);\n\n  const toggleRule = (id: string) => {\n    // Simulated state change\n    setRules(rules.map(r => r.id === id ? { ...r, status: r.status === \"verified\" ? \"warning\" : \"verified\" } : r));\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <WorkspaceCard className=\"space-y-4\">\n      <div className=\"flex flex-wrap justify-between items-start gap-3 border-b border-white/5 pb-3 select-none\">\n        <div>\n          <h4 className=\"text-[14px] font-bold text-white font-mono tracking-wider uppercase\">Active Guardrails Ledger</h4>\n          <p className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/45 mt-1\">Verified ISO/SOC policy rulesets actively checked in real time.</p>\n        </div>\n        <StatusBadge state=\"active\" label=\"all compliant\" />\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"space-y-3 font-mono text-[11.5px]\">\n        {rules.map(rule => (\n          <div \n            key={rule.id}\n            onClick={() => toggleRule(rule.id)}\n            className=\"flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#020202]/30 hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-[#020202]/60 transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n          >\n            {rule.status === \"verified\" ? (\n              <CheckCircle className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#00FFC2] shrink-0 mt-0.5\" />\n            ) : (\n              <AlertCircle className=\"w-4 h-4 text-amber-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5\" />\n            )}\n            <div>\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                <span className=\"font-bold text-white\">{rule.name}</span>\n                <span className={`text-[9px] px-1 py-0.1 border rounded ${rule.status === \"verified\" ? \"text-[#00FFC2] bg-[#00FFC2]/5 border-[#00FFC2]/20\" : \"text-amber-400 bg-amber-400/5 border-amber-400/20\"}`}>\n                  {rule.status === \"verified\" ? \"LOCKED\" : \"EVAL\"}\n                </span>\n              </div>\n              <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 mt-1 leading-normal\">{rule.desc}</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        ))}\n      </div>\n    </WorkspaceCard>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 20. AGENT HEALTH CARD (Dense console diagnostics)\n// ==========================================\nexport interface AgentSpec {\n  id: string;\n  name: string;\n  status: \"verified\" | \"evaluating\" | \"decoupled\";\n  threads: number;\n  memory: string;\n  logs: string[];\n}\n\nexport function AgentHealthCard({ \n  agent,\n  onRestart\n}: { \n  agent: AgentSpec;\n  onRestart?: () => void;\n}) {\n  const [rebooting, setRebooting] = useState(false);\n  const [activeLogs, setActiveLogs] = useState<string[]>(agent.logs);\n\n  const triggerReboot = () => {\n    setRebooting(true);\n    setActiveLogs(prev => [...prev, `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] INITIATING HARDWARE REBOOT SEQUENCE...`]);\n    \n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setRebooting(false);\n      setActiveLogs(prev => [\n        ...prev, \n        `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] REBOOT COMPLETED SUCCESSFULLY`,\n        `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] MEMORY SECTORS RE-ALIGNED`,\n        `[${new Date().toLocaleTimeString()}] CRYPTOGRAPHIC BOUNDARY LOCK ESTABLISHED`\n      ]);\n      if (onRestart) onRestart();\n    }, 1800);\n  };\n\n  return (\n    <WorkspaceCard className=\"space-y-4\">\n      <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start border-b border-white/5 pb-3.5 select-none\">\n        <div>\n          <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-[#009DFF] bg-[#009DFF]/5 border border-[#009DFF]/20 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded\">\n            AGENT DIAGNOSTIC\n          </span>\n          <h4 className=\"text-[14px] font-bold text-white font-mono mt-1.5\">{agent.name}</h4>\n        </div>\n        <StatusBadge \n          state={rebooting ? \"warning\" : agent.status === \"verified\" ? \"active\" : \"decoupled\"} \n          label={rebooting ? \"REBOOTING\" : agent.status} \n        />\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 font-mono text-[11px] select-none\">\n        <div className=\"p-2.5 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01]\">\n          <span className=\"text-white/35 block text-[9px] uppercase\">Active Threads</span>\n          <span className=\"text-white font-bold block mt-0.5\">{agent.threads} CORE LOOPS</span>\n        </div>\n        <div className=\"p-2.5 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01]\">\n          <span className=\"text-white/35 block text-[9px] uppercase\">Context Cache</span>\n          <span className=\"text-white font-bold block mt-0.5\">{agent.memory}</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Embedded Terminal Logs */}\n      <div className=\"border border-white/5 rounded-lg overflow-hidden bg-black/60 p-3 h-32 overflow-y-auto font-mono text-[10px] text-white/60 space-y-1\">\n        {activeLogs.map((log, idx) => (\n          <div key={idx} className=\"leading-relaxed\">\n            <span className=\"text-white/30 mr-1.5 select-none\">&gt;&gt;</span>\n            <span className={log.includes(\"REBOOT\") || log.includes(\"EXCHANGING\") ? \"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\" : log.includes(\"SUCCESSFULLY\") ? \"text-emerald-400 font-bold\" : \"\"}>\n              {log}\n            </span>\n          </div>\n        ))}\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n        <button \n          onClick={triggerReboot}\n          disabled={rebooting}\n          className=\"flex-grow inline-flex h-8 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 rounded border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.01] text-[10.5px] font-bold text-white hover:bg-white/[0.04] hover:border-white/25 transition-all disabled:opacity-50 cursor-pointer select-none font-mono\"\n        >\n          {rebooting ? (\n            <>\n              <RefreshCw className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 animate-spin text-[#009DFF]\" />\n              <span>CYCLING HARDWARE...</span>\n            </>\n          ) : (\n            <>\n              <RefreshCw className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n              <span>RECYCLE CORE ENCLAVE</span>\n            </>\n          )}\n        </button>\n      </div>\n    </WorkspaceCard>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 21. PROJECT CARD (Integrated Workspace sandbox)\n// ==========================================\nexport interface ProjectSpec {\n  id: string;\n  name: string;\n  status: \"verified\" | \"evaluating\";\n  desc: string;\n  nodesCount: number;\n  lastUpdated: string;\n}\n\nexport function ProjectCard({ \n  project \n}: { \n  project: ProjectSpec;\n}) {\n  return (\n    <WorkspaceCard className=\"flex flex-col h-full justify-between\">\n      <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n        <div className=\"flex justify-between items-start select-none\">\n          <div className=\"p-2 rounded bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400\">\n            <Layers className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n          </div>\n          <StatusBadge state={project.status === \"verified\" ? \"active\" : \"warning\"} label={project.status} />\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <h4 className=\"text-[13.5px] font-bold text-white font-mono tracking-tight\">{project.name.toUpperCase()}</h4>\n          <p className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-white/50 mt-1 leading-relaxed\">{project.desc}</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"border-t border-white/5 pt-3 mt-4 space-y-2 font-mono text-[10.5px] select-none\">\n        <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n          <span className=\"text-white/40\">Registered Nodes:</span>\n          <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{project.nodesCount} CLUSTERS</span>\n        </div>\n        <div className=\"flex justify-between\">\n          <span className=\"text-white/40\">Sync State:</span>\n          <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold uppercase\">Synced</span>\n        </div>\n        <div className=\"flex justify-between text-[9.5px] text-white/35 pt-1.5\">\n          <span>LAST COMPLIANCE RUN:</span>\n          <span>{project.lastUpdated}</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </WorkspaceCard>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 22. PRIVATE TOPBAR\n// ==========================================\nexport function PrivateTopbar({ \n  user,\n  breadcrumbs,\n  onSearchClick,\n  role,\n  onRoleChange,\n  onToggleSidebar\n}: { \n  user: UserProfile;\n  breadcrumbs: BreadcrumbItem[];\n  onSearchClick: () => void;\n  role: \"Client\" | \"Administrator\";\n  onRoleChange: (role: \"Client\" | \"Administrator\") => void;\n  onToggleSidebar: () => void;\n}) {\n  return (\n    <header className=\"sticky top-0 z-30 flex h-14 w-full items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/80 px-4 md:px-6 backdrop-blur-md select-none\">\n      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n        <button \n          onClick={onToggleSidebar}\n          className=\"flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-white/5 hover:border-white/15 hover:bg-white/[0.03] lg:hidden text-white/80 hover:text-white cursor-pointer\"\n          aria-label=\"Toggle navigation menu\"\n        >\n          <Menu className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n        </button>\n        <div className=\"hidden sm:block\">\n          <WorkspaceBreadcrumbs items={breadcrumbs} />\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3\">\n        <WorkspaceCommandButton onClick={onSearchClick} />\n        <RoleSwitcherPreview currentRole={role} onRoleChange={onRoleChange} />\n        <NotificationBell />\n        <div className=\"border-l border-white/10 h-6 mx-0.5 hidden md:block\" />\n        <UserAvatar user={user} showDetails={true} />\n      </div>\n    </header>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 23. PRIVATE SIDEBAR\n// ==========================================\nexport interface SidebarLink {\n  id: string;\n  label: string;\n  desc: string;\n  icon: React.ComponentType<{ className?: string }>;\n}\n\nexport function PrivateSidebar({ \n  links,\n  activeLink,\n  onLinkChange,\n  collapsed,\n  onToggleCollapse,\n  user,\n  role\n}: { \n  links: SidebarLink[];\n  activeLink: string;\n  onLinkChange: (id: string) => void;\n  collapsed: boolean;\n  onToggleCollapse: () => void;\n  user: UserProfile;\n  role: \"Client\" | \"Administrator\";\n}) {\n  return (\n    <aside \n      className={`hidden lg:flex flex-col h-screen shrink-0 border-r border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/65 backdrop-blur-md select-none transition-all duration-300 ${collapsed ? \"w-20\" : \"w-64\"}`}\n    >\n      {/* Brand space */}\n      <div className=\"h-14 border-b border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between px-5\">\n        <Link href=\"/\" className=\"flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer group\">\n          <div className=\"h-6 w-6 rounded border border-[#009DFF]/30 bg-[#009DFF]/5 flex items-center justify-center text-[#009DFF] group-hover:border-[#009DFF]/50 transition-all\">\n            <Lock className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n          </div>\n          {!collapsed && (\n            <span className=\"text-[14px] font-black font-mono tracking-widest text-white leading-none\">\n              GFF <span className=\"text-[#009DFF]\">AI</span>\n            </span>\n          )}\n        </Link>\n        <button \n          onClick={onToggleCollapse}\n          className=\"text-white/20 hover:text-white/50 text-[10px] hidden lg:block cursor-pointer\"\n        >\n          {collapsed ? <ChevronRight className=\"w-4 h-4\" /> : <ChevronDown className=\"w-4 h-4 -rotate-90\" />}\n        </button>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Nav groups */}\n      <div className=\"flex-grow p-4 overflow-y-auto space-y-6\">\n        <div className=\"space-y-1.5\">\n          {!collapsed && (\n            <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono font-bold tracking-widest text-white/25 px-2 block select-none uppercase\">\n              {role === \"Client\" ? \"Client Workspace\" : \"Oversight Console\"}\n            </span>\n          )}\n          {links.map((link) => {\n            const Icon = link.icon;\n            const isActive = activeLink === link.id;\n            return (\n              <button\n                key={link.id}\n                onClick={() => onLinkChange(link.id)}\n                className={`w-full flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-left transition-all cursor-pointer group ${isActive ? \"bg-white/10 text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/25 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,157,255,0.02)]\" : \"text-white/55 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/[0.02] border border-transparent\"}`}\n              >\n                <Icon className={`w-4 h-4 shrink-0 transition-colors ${isActive ? \"text-[#009DFF]\" : \"text-white/40 group-hover:text-white\"}`} />\n                {!collapsed && (\n                  <div>\n                    <span className=\"text-[12px] font-bold block\">{link.label}</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono text-white/30 block mt-0.5 leading-none font-normal\">{link.desc}</span>\n                  </div>\n                )}\n              </button>\n            );\n          })}\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Footer info block */}\n      {!collapsed && (\n        <div className=\"p-4 border-t border-white/5 bg-black/20 text-center font-mono text-[9px] text-white/25 select-none\">\n          SECURE SECURE CLOCK: 2026.06.27\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </aside>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 24. PRIVATE PAGE HEADER\n// ==========================================\nexport function PrivatePageHeader({ \n  title, \n  desc, \n  badgeLabel = \"SOC2 Enclave\",\n  actions \n}: { \n  title: string; \n  desc: string; \n  badgeLabel?: string;\n  actions?: React.ReactNode;\n}) {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-center gap-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-5 select-none\">\n      <div>\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n          <h1 className=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white\">{title}</h1>\n          <span className=\"inline-flex rounded bg-[#009DFF]/10 border border-[#009DFF]/20 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[9px] font-mono font-bold uppercase text-[#009DFF]\">\n            {badgeLabel}\n          </span>\n        </div>\n        <p className=\"text-[12.5px] text-white/50 font-mono mt-1 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl\">{desc}</p>\n      </div>\n\n      {actions && (\n        <div className=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2.5 shrink-0 w-full md:w-auto\">\n          {actions}\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n\n// ==========================================\n// 25. PRIVATE APP SHELL (Combines everything)\n// ==========================================\nexport function PrivateAppShell({ \n  children,\n  user,\n  breadcrumbs,\n  links,\n  activeLink,\n  onLinkChange,\n  role,\n  onRoleChange\n}: { \n  children: React.ReactNode;\n  user: UserProfile;\n  breadcrumbs: BreadcrumbItem[];\n  links: SidebarLink[];\n  activeLink: string;\n  onLinkChange: (id: string) => void;\n  role: \"Client\" | \"Administrator\";\n  onRoleChange: (role: \"Client\" | \"Administrator\") => void;\n}) {\n  const [sidebarCollapsed, setSidebarCollapsed] = useState(false);\n  const [mobileSidebarOpen, setMobileSidebarOpen] = useState(false);\n  const [commandPaletteOpen, setCommandPaletteOpen] = useState(false);\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"min-h-screen flex bg-[#030303] text-white overflow-x-hidden\">\n      {/* 1. Secure banner notice */}\n      <div className=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50\">\n        <SecurePreviewNotice />\n      </div>\n\n      <div className=\"pt-8 w-full flex\">\n        {/* 2. Desktop Sidebar */}\n        <PrivateSidebar \n          links={links}\n          activeLink={activeLink}\n          onLinkChange={(id) => {\n            onLinkChange(id);\n            setMobileSidebarOpen(false);\n          }}\n          collapsed={sidebarCollapsed}\n          onToggleCollapse={() => setSidebarCollapsed(!sidebarCollapsed)}\n          user={user}\n          role={role}\n        />\n\n        {/* 3. Mobile Sidebar slide-out Drawer */}\n        <AnimatePresence>\n          {mobileSidebarOpen && (\n            <>\n              <motion.div \n                initial={{ opacity: 0 }}\n                animate={{ opacity: 0.5 }}\n                exit={{ opacity: 0 }}\n                className=\"fixed inset-0 z-40 bg-black lg:hidden\"\n                onClick={() => setMobileSidebarOpen(false)}\n              />\n              <motion.div \n                initial={{ x: \"-100%\" }}\n                animate={{ x: 0 }}\n                exit={{ x: \"-100%\" }}\n                transition={{ type: \"spring\", bounce: 0, duration: 0.3 }}\n                className=\"fixed inset-y-0 left-0 z-50 w-72 bg-[#050505] border-r border-white/5 flex flex-col pt-8\"\n              >\n                <div className=\"h-14 border-b border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between px-5 select-none\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[14px] font-black font-mono tracking-widest text-white leading-none\">\n                    GFF <span className=\"text-[#009DFF]\">AI</span>\n                  </span>\n                  <button \n                    onClick={() => setMobileSidebarOpen(false)}\n                    className=\"text-white/40 hover:text-white\"\n                  >\n                    <X className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n                  </button>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"flex-grow p-4 overflow-y-auto space-y-4\">\n                  <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                    {links.map((link) => {\n                      const Icon = link.icon;\n                      const isActive = activeLink === link.id;\n                      return (\n                        <button\n                          key={link.id}\n                          onClick={() => {\n                            onLinkChange(link.id);\n                            setMobileSidebarOpen(false);\n                          }}\n                          className={`w-full flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg text-left transition-colors ${isActive ? \"bg-white/10 text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/15\" : \"text-white/60 hover:text-white\"}`}\n                        >\n                          <Icon className=\"w-4.5 h-4.5 text-white/40\" />\n                          <div>\n                            <span className=\"text-[12.5px] font-bold block\">{link.label}</span>\n                            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30 block mt-0.5 font-normal\">{link.desc}</span>\n                          </div>\n                        </button>\n                      );\n                    })}\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </motion.div>\n            </>\n          )}\n        </AnimatePresence>\n\n        {/* 4. Main viewport context */}\n        <div className=\"flex-grow flex flex-col min-h-[calc(100vh-2rem)] min-w-0\">\n          <PrivateTopbar \n            user={user}\n            breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}\n            onSearchClick={() => setCommandPaletteOpen(true)}\n            role={role}\n            onRoleChange={onRoleChange}\n            onToggleSidebar={() => setMobileSidebarOpen(true)}\n          />\n\n          <main className=\"flex-grow p-4 md:p-6 lg:p-8 space-y-8 overflow-y-auto\">\n            {children}\n          </main>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* 5. Central Command Search Dialog */}\n      <CommandPalette \n        isOpen={commandPaletteOpen} \n        onClose={() => setCommandPaletteOpen(false)} \n        onNavigate={onLinkChange}\n      />\n    </div>\n  );\n}"}}}
